# Restaurant Website — Implementation Plan

A premium restaurant landing site built with **Next.js 14 App Router**, **Tailwind CSS**, **React Three Fiber**, and **Framer Motion** — featuring a 3D hero scene, scroll-triggered animations, reservation system, and a protected admin dashboard.

---

## Tech Stack

| Layer | Technology |
|-------|-----------|
| Frontend | Next.js 14 (App Router), React 18 |
| Styling | Tailwind CSS v3, custom CSS vars |
| 3D | React Three Fiber + Drei + Three.js |
| Animations | Framer Motion |
| Backend | Next.js API Routes (no separate Express needed) |
| Data Store | JSON file DB via `fs` (easily swappable to Postgres/MongoDB) |
| Auth | JWT stored in HTTP-only cookie (admin only) |
| Fonts | Google Fonts — Playfair Display + Inter |
| Deploy | Vercel (frontend + API routes) |

---

