## Proposed Changes

### Core Setup

#### [NEW] package.json — Dependencies
- `next`, `react`, `react-dom`
- `@react-three/fiber`, `@react-three/drei`, `three`
- `framer-motion`
- `tailwindcss`, `postcss`, `autoprefixer`
- `jsonwebtoken`, `bcryptjs`, `cookie`
- `@types/*` for TypeScript

---

### Pages & Components

#### [NEW] app/layout.tsx
Root layout: imports Playfair Display + Inter from Google Fonts, wraps `<body>` with `Navbar` and `Footer`, adds a `PageTransition` Framer Motion wrapper.

#### [NEW] app/page.tsx — Home
- **Hero section**: full-viewport with `HeroScene` (R3F).  3D rotating food bowl/plate model with scroll-linked Y-rotation using `useScroll` from Drei.  Floating ambient particles.  Headline text fades in on load.
- **About teaser**: stitch-style overlapping layered cards with `SectionReveal`.
- **Featured dishes**: 3-column card grid with hover lift + image zoom effect.
- **CTA banner**: parallax background with booking prompt.

#### [NEW] components/HeroScene.tsx
React Three Fiber canvas with:
- A custom `<FloatingDish>` mesh (torus-knot placeholder, replaceable with GLTF)
- `useScroll` hook → maps scroll offset to mesh rotation
- Ambient + point lights with warm restaurant tones
- `OrbitControls` (damping only, auto-rotate) via Drei
- Postprocessing: bloom effect via `@react-three/postprocessing`

#### [NEW] app/menu/page.tsx
- Category tabs (Starters, Mains, Desserts, Drinks) with Framer Motion `AnimatePresence` for item grid transitions
- Each `MenuCard` has: image, name, price, description, dietary tags
- Fetch from `/api/menu`

#### [NEW] app/reservations/page.tsx
- Multi-step form: Step 1 (date/time/guests) → Step 2 (name/phone/email/notes)
- Framer Motion step transitions (slide left/right)
- Submit → POST `/api/reservations` → success animation (checkmark Lottie / CSS)

#### [NEW] app/contact/page.tsx
- Animated contact info cards (phone, email, address) with staggered slide-in
- Google Maps embed
- Contact form with motion

#### [NEW] app/admin/login/page.tsx
- Clean centered login form
- POST to `/api/admin/login`, set JWT cookie, redirect to `/admin/dashboard`

#### [NEW] app/admin/dashboard/page.tsx
- Server-side JWT cookie check (redirect if not authenticated)
- Tab UI: Menu Management | Reservations
- `MenuEditor`: add/edit/delete dishes, optimistic UI updates
- `ReservationViewer`: list all reservations with status

---

### API Routes

#### [NEW] app/api/menu/route.ts — `GET /api/menu`
Returns all menu items from `data/menu.json`

#### [NEW] app/api/reservations/route.ts — `POST /api/reservations`
Validates input, appends to `data/reservations.json`, returns 201

#### [NEW] app/api/admin/login/route.ts — `POST /api/admin/login`
Checks credentials (env vars `ADMIN_USER`, `ADMIN_PASS`), signs JWT, sets `HttpOnly` cookie

#### [NEW] app/api/admin/menu/route.ts — `GET/POST/PUT/DELETE /api/admin/menu`
Full CRUD on `data/menu.json` — protected by JWT middleware

#### [NEW] app/api/admin/reservations/route.ts — `GET /api/admin/reservations`
Returns all reservations — protected

---

### Data & Auth

#### [NEW] data/menu.json
Seed data with 12 menu items across 4 categories

#### [NEW] data/reservations.json
Empty array initially, written to by the POST API

#### [NEW] lib/auth.ts
`signToken(payload)` and `verifyToken(token)` using `jsonwebtoken`

#### [NEW] lib/db.ts
`readJSON(file)` and `writeJSON(file, data)` helpers using Node `fs`

---

## Verification Plan

### Automated
- `npm run build` — must succeed with 0 TypeScript errors
- `npm run lint` — must pass ESLint

### Browser Testing (via browser subagent)
1. `npm run dev` → open `http://localhost:3000`
2. Verify hero 3D scene renders and model rotates on scroll
3. Navigate to `/menu` — test category tab switching
4. Navigate to `/reservations` — fill form, submit, verify success animation
5. Navigate to `/contact` — check map embed and animations
6. Navigate to `/admin/login` — login with test credentials
7. In `/admin/dashboard` — add a new menu item, verify it appears on `/menu`

### Environment Variables Required
```
ADMIN_USER=admin
ADMIN_PASS=restaurant123
JWT_SECRET=your_super_secret_key_here
```
